              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The fluorine target was obtained by vacuum evaporation",
                "of MnF2 onto a 3 mg/cm2 gold foil, the thickness of",
                "gold being chosen to prevent the 19Ne nuclei recoiling",
                "out of the target and being lost from the counting",
                "region. The target thickness was determined as follows.",
                "A piece of thick aluminium foil was placed alongside",
                "the gold backing during the evaporation of the MnF2",
                "target, and the thickness of MnF2 deposited was",
                "determined by observing the apparent energy shift of",
                "the 773 keV 27Al(p,g)28Si resonance when the proton",
                "beam, obtained from the accelerator, passed through",
                "the MnF2 layer. The content of fluorine was calculated",
                "as 19.5+-2.5 mu-g/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
